Google Maps (turn on lat/long tooltips in Maps Labs)

http://srtm.csi.cgiar.org/

    wget http://srtm.csi.cgiar.org/SRT-ZIP/SRTM_v41/SRTM_Data_ArcASCII/srtm_44_13.zip
OR  wget ftp://xftp.jrc.it/pub/srtmV4/arcasci/srtm_44_13.zip

    unzip srtm_44_13.zip

Mont Blanc

    terrain -i srtm_30_03.asc -c 45.8334,6.8650

Mount Kilimanjaro

    terrain -c -3.076,37.35 -s 1500x1500 -b 600 srtm_44_13.asc

Ben Nevis (crosses two input files):

    terrain -c 56.812,-4.99 srtm_35_01.asc srtm_36_01.asc
